History.The Grand Tour of the Realms:
In the 1360s DR, Eric and his friends visited the town of [[Shadowdale (town)|Shadowdale]] in [[Faerûn]] so that Presto could ask the great sage [[Elminster]] to take him on as an apprentice. While drinking in the [[Old Skull Inn]], they spotted Elminster, but Eric dismissed him as old and insisted that wizards often told lies to make themselves appear more important. When Presto lost his nerve, Eric taunted him by making [[chicken]] noises, yet stood beside him to declare his suitability to Elminster.{{Cite comic/Forgotten Realms: The Grand Tour}}

Thus, Elminster whisked Presto away on a whirlwind tour of the Realms, and he came back traumatized and beaten and decided it best not to be his apprentice. Nevertheless, Presto had ideas for future adventures with his friends.

At this time, Eric was a middle-aged adult and wore a blue [[cloak]] over his dark-brown clothing.
